title: Yheti Discography (2008-2014)
description:
Yheti is an electronic music producer located in Dayton, Ohio.Producing predominately bass music, Yheti's sound is like no other!Describing his own sets as "A dynamic soul massage of awkward bass intensities" Yheti is definitely one to check out and has been kind enough to provide his complete discography!


This complete Yheti discography includes 147 tracks and mixes released over the past 5 years.Including all track released under his previous alias Yeti Master.Be sure to share with any friends you think may enjoy his music and to follow him on all social media outlets!
